                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City-policeman</hi>, 553.) I took the prisoner—he said a man stopped him in the street, and said he would give him sixpence to carry the cloth to Petticoat-lane.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. A man asked me to carry it, and said he would give me sixpence; I was out of work, and did so.</p>
